            <description><![CDATA[<h2>ChainLink 0.3.629</h2>
<p class="sub">A small follow-up to 0.3.628.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Sharing ChainLink with a friend now uses a single link that works on iPhone, iPad and Mac
  (Settings → Invite a tester).</li>
  <li>Includes everything from 0.3.628 — Bike Fit geometry lookup, the web-searching coach,
  the saddle-to-bar safety check, and the latest Gemini model.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
